					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="1280" height="857" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shepherd-dog-4357790_1280.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shepherd-dog-4357790_1280.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shepherd-dog-4357790_1280.jpg?resize=768%2C514&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shepherd-dog-4357790_1280.jpg?resize=218%2C146&amp;ssl=1 218w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
